<p>Kana Imuta and Damian Scarf (2014) <em>When too much of a novel thing may be what&#8217;s “bad”: commentary on Fisher, Godwin, and Seltman (2014</em>) <strong>Frontiers of Psychology</strong>, 23 December 2014,  doi.org/10.3389/fpsyg.2014.01444</p>
